<td class="mbox-text" style="">
<div>
<div style="text-align:left;"><b>This article has multiple issues.</b> Please help <b><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Shoplifting&amp;action=edit" class="external text" title="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Shoplifting&amp;action=edit" rel="nofollow">improve the article</a></b> or discuss these issues on the <b><a href="/wiki/Talk:Shoplifting" title="Talk:Shoplifting">talk page</a></b>.</div>
