<li>It may not present a <b><a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:WikiProject_Countering_systemic_bias" title="Wikipedia:WikiProject Countering systemic bias">worldwide view</a></b> of the subject. <small>Tagged since August 2008.</small><br /></li>
